org.cef.network

Class CefPostData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.network.CefPostData

  • public abstract class CefPostData
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to represent post data for a web request. The methods of this class may be called on any thread.(用于表示web请求的post数据的类。这个类的方法可以在任何线程上调用。)
